  "body": "<p>The <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/block-party?aff=6cc2c70f\">Block Party kit along with all the add-on's</a> are sold out. Hope you were lucky enough to get your hands on some of the good stuff. Here is how this layout came together.</p><p>Inky Black Mister Huey's is one of my favorite colors. The splatters turn out perfect.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"9a-DSC_0917-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/104aa4354508a74c.jpg?v=1782536669\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"9b-DSC_0920-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6cd19b31b1d779cd.jpg?v=1782536672\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9c-DSC_0921-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8d44178064451edb.jpg?v=1782536674\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9d-DSC_0922-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6f44f6f48f4f73a8.jpg?v=1782536677\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9e-DSC_0923-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/11055dac3ccbafae.jpg?v=1782536680\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9f-DSC_0924-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/929e44fab2b7f992.jpg?v=1782536683\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"9g-welcomehomeSC-561x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a47ab87333cca42e.jpg?v=1782536685\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>You can see all the layouts from the January kit in the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/block-party/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">SC Scrapbook Gallery</a>.</p>"
